beer.beer_description:
Jester | Chinook | Motueka

We know we’re all about the haze. But sometimes, you just can't beat a proper West Coast IPA, right? Tree Line is our excuse to brew another crisp one, featuring our beloved Chinook and a newbie for us: Jester. Now, Jester's not a typical hop in our brewery, especially since it's a modern UK variety we're still getting to know. But with notes of grapefruit, tropical fruit, and blackcurrant being thrown around, we were sold! Keen to hear what you reckon.

items.badge_description: Thanks for staying at home, and checking in with Untappd! It allows us to stay connected to a community of beer lovers, just like you, even if we can't be in the same physical location. From our home to yours, cheers and stay safe!

While spontaneity can be fun, sometimes you want to make sure your adventure will rock. Checkout the menu at an Untappd Verified Venue before visiting and know exactly what’s on tap! That's 85 check-ins at venue that is verified. Try 5 more for Level 18!

Canning is all the rage and it's not hard to see why - travels well, more environmentally friendly, and no need to carry your bottle opener. That's 80 checkins with the serving style of Can. Try 5 more for Level 17! Want to learn more about this badge? Check out our podcast
We believe in IPA and you should too. You certainly have a taste for the hops! That's 70 different IPAs. Try 5 more for Level 15! Want to learn more about this badge? Check out our podcast
